  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Admin Executive (Depot)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Description</strong></p>\n<p>Cogent Holdings Pte Ltd is a subsidiary of Cosco Shipping International (Singapore) Co., Ltd and has a wide range of clientele ranging from local SMEs to multinational companies. Cogent owns one of Singapore's largest one-stop integrated logistics hub, Cogent 1.Logistics Hub. It offers warehousing, freight forwarding, container and ISO tank depot, automotive logistics, and transportation services in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Role Description</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for an <strong>Admin Executive</strong> in <strong>Cogent Tank Depot Pte Ltd</strong>. This role will be responsible for seamless inventory management, oversee incoming and outgoing container movement and coordinate with customers.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist the Manager to ensure that all procedures and requirements are adhered to</li>\n  <li>Monitor the bookings, daily transactions and customer instructions (returning/collection) for smooth operation</li>\n  <li>Attend to daily mail correspondences from customers</li>\n  <li>Discuss and report to manager on enhancement of daily operations and assist the manager in implementation of productivity initiatives</li>\n  <li>Report to manager should there be any discrepancies, non-compliance, accidents or escalation from customers</li>\n  <li>Assist the manager in maintaining staff discipline in the office</li>\n  <li>Ensure parts and equipment’s availability, inventory and procedural flow integrity and functionality</li>\n  <li>Maintain customer requirements and confidence</li>\n  <li>Observe performance and resolve difficulties pertaining to inadequate response to movement requirements and daily inventory supply</li>\n  <li>Attend the regular operation meeting with customers to discuss operations work plan and schedule</li>\n  <li>Keep track of fixed assets and ensure depot facilities are in good order</li>\n  <li>Liaise with trucking vendors on delivery reliability</li>\n  <li>Regulate the accuracy and priority of jobs undertaken and timely billing by office team</li>\n  <li>Implement and manage systems records, implementation and customization</li>\n  <li>Any other duties and responsibilities assigned from time to time</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma or equivalent qualification</li>\n  <li>Preferably with 2 years relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Able work under a fast-paced work environment</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Willing to work in Jurong Island</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Other Information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monday to Friday: 8.30am – 5.15pm; Alternate Saturday: 8.30am – 3.15pm</li>\n  <li>Lunch provided</li>\n  <li>Medical, dental &amp; insurance benefits</li>\n  <li>2-ways company transport provided from Lakeside MRT</li>\n</ul>",
